Marian McCargo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marian_McCargo 0 Marian McCargo Bell (March 18, 1932 – April 7, 2004) was an American actress and champion tennis player who later found success in film and television roles. She was sometimes credited as Marian Moses.
